{"id":"bf546d808013639f7024aab686f05a2d101785f5bd4c036c5b0c3d2056506f15","item_id":"535f6211ea:0","text":"1. 在 OUT context（OUT 上下文）中，插入一个 denoise node（降噪节点），并将 RenderMan ROP node 连接到该 denoise node。"}
{"id":"f80c646af40ba53ebd2550c8748c49c0558e577dfce99262288dac34d6ffb7ff","item_id":"535f6211ea:1","text":"2. 在 RenderMan ROP 的 Images 下，取消勾选"}
{"id":"68eee93838c3c01dd197552fff78b71730025a34ad4d37060afea70d12388ca6","item_id":"535f6211ea:2","text":"as RGBA（作为 RGBA）"}
{"id":"ea7fdc00423772003dda75272b78b41048611d650c6ce81384e32f18b6f5fa43","item_id":"535f6211ea:3","text":"并选择"}
{"id":"f6a472cd40532137ebfcb05358ce32a433f343a156a30519b7fa5bb85a014d68","item_id":"535f6211ea:4","text":"Denoise（降噪）"}
{"id":"8849b03250cc111fcebbbc80122f1641ff21aac9a72620140598f9af78f9758d","item_id":"535f6211ea:5","text":"3. 选择"}
{"id":"bc56bb075d0cd5f5f26ccd7626d9c56da3a685ad4f4fc60bda9eee978f744d4f","item_id":"535f6211ea:6","text":"denoise（降噪）"}
{"id":"97ec946ef5a1f3877f5fc4c991075a77d9eb93fd39f765acafc5b99ccf721220","item_id":"535f6211ea:7","text":"node（节点），并设置 mode type（模式类型）、output location（输出位置）、Asymmetry、Flow 和 debug options（调试选项）；准备好渲染后，按下 Denoise 按钮。"}
{"id":"48ee582d4fd44a9cc66ea6c307577303b6a3f09a554076e0ad7f4d8afe098794","item_id":"535f6211ea:8","text":"要 render frame(s)（渲染帧），点击 Denoise，Houdini 会随后渲染 frame(s)；当所有 frames 都渲染完成后，denoise process（降噪流程）会开始。"}
{"id":"79395313322fbaca759eecba8e8ed484113a6eea3f66cecfa8628d0abf2edc36","item_id":"535f6211ea:9","text":"Gotcha（注意事项）"}
{"id":"e94bf69b57a09ae59e26ef8d45dbd26922fc9612ae1fdf9107b6d993eb9184e2","item_id":"535f6211ea:10","text":"虽然这听起来很明显，但请务必在文件名中添加 $F4，否则 denoiser（降噪器）会失败，即使你只渲染单帧也是如此。"}
